{"tid":1002800,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵客瞓過龍　車長疑「崩潰」開咪狂嗌︰起身喇！","createTime":"2019-01-31T08:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T13:32:38.000Z","uid":225464,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6eb3a24c176daa39cf0f227942d821bd6957bba5","tid":1002800,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:00:43.000Z","msg":"<strong>港鐵客瞓過龍　車長疑「崩潰」開咪狂嗌︰起身喇！</strong><br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://buff.ly/2sXIjWQ[/url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuff.ly%2F2sXIjWQ%5B%2Furl&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6mrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=3db5bf5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buff.ly/2sXIjWQ[/url</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190131/photo/bkn-20190131131940412-0131_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190131133906\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190131%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190131131940412-0131_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190131133906&h=e2ad5607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n生活忙碌，搭車難免小睡片刻。但近日有港鐵乘客疑瞓過龍，當列車到終點站時仍未起身，車長遂「大開金口」，大嗌︰「夠鐘喇！起身喇」！<br />\n<br />\n片段於星期四（31日）上傳至Facebook群組「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」，在港鐵北角站內有列車打開門停在月台，有乘客疑在車廂內熟睡，僅餘寥寥數人的月台不斷傳來疑似車長的廣播︰「好早咋，十點半喇，唔好瞓喇喂！喂！喂！到站喇，起身喇，喂」。<br />\n<br />\n月台隨後亦「配合」地再發廣播︰「列車已經到達終點站，請盡快離開車廂，多謝合作」，惟車廂內仍未見動靜。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛表示搞笑，戲言︰「好似老竇叫仔起身返學咁」、「錄低佢做鬧鐘響聲，包醒」。有人則稱讚事件有「人情味」︰「證明車長係有血有肉，唔係冷冰冰嘅地鐵」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好搞笑"},{"pid":"abe48a9ebd206933bce149cd15661789d82888aa","tid":1002800,"uid":106233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:09:43.000Z","msg":"個車長叫得好有磁性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ce43c80d738bab7629f64252266289a1c6481c","tid":1002800,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:11:36.000Z","msg":"突然覺得好溫暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0e0583df7ee39dd32c459dc78c20aba389b5a6","tid":1002800,"uid":12021,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:58:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9b3f323917e4f28ffc1f1e56a5b1a7cb7ac39d5","tid":1002800,"uid":7482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:35:42.000Z","msg":"以前都試過 有個staff 黎拍醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢驚到仆街以為我暈左"},{"pid":"06b6d5da1fe9e2b4860ad37d3a9e61efb531b70b","tid":1002800,"uid":209189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e3b30c98ff74351f95fb7b09c735460213390b","tid":1002800,"uid":193131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢叫到好似條友唔起身就冇得收工咁"},{"pid":"f9f5d97bc37a11492a15fcf2b1938717bb5cc031","tid":1002800,"uid":12877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:16:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190131/bkn-20190131131940412-0131_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190131%2Fbkn-20190131131940412-0131_00822_001.html&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6mrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=73f3b57d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190131/bkn-20190131131940412-0131_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5af45550dd42dc94ce1ae6455895a3cb88777992","tid":1002800,"uid":196252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:21:19.000Z","msg":"把聲唔錯<br />\n幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f05aa523279fbab8628e4bda1d35deec58fc26","tid":1002800,"uid":28588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT